  <package>nice.ui.common</package>

  <shortDescription>Extension of the Swing toolkit to make use of Nice advanced features</shortDescription>

  <description>
    This library allows you to write a Swing user interface in Nice programs.
    It allows a more elegant programming style than Swing programs written in
    Java by using Nice's features like anonymous functions and named 
    and optional method parameters.
  </description>

